      "@id": "https://data.datatourisme.fr/9b66cada-8fb6-3aef-af76-62d6c2053ed2",
      "dc:description": {
        "de": [
          "Der Delphin-Club empfängt Ihre Kinder ab 3 Jahren. Animationen, traditionelle Spiele, Trampoline, Seilrutschen\r\nSchwimmen ab 4 Jahren im beheizten Pool.\r\nPerfektionierung im Meer.\r\nEinführung in die Küstenrettung."
        ],
        "en": [
          "The Dolphin Club welcomes children aged 3 and over. Activities, traditional games, trampolines, tyrolean traverse, etc\r\nSwimming from age 4 in heated pool.\r\nPerfecting your swimming skills at sea.\r\nIntroduction to coastal lifesaving."
        ],
        "it": [
          "Il Club dei Delfini accoglie i bambini dai 3 anni in su. Attività, giochi tradizionali, trampolini, teleferiche, ecc\r\nNuoto a partire dai 4 anni in una piscina riscaldata.\r\nPerfezionamento delle abilità di nuoto in mare.\r\nIntroduzione al salvataggio costiero."
        ],
        "fr": [
          "Le club des dauphins accueille vos enfants dès 3 ans. Animations, jeux traditionnels, trampolines, tyrolienne\r\nNatation dès 4ans en piscine chauffée.\r\nPerfectionnement en mer.\r\nInitiation sauvetage côtier."
        ],
        "es": [
          "El Club de los Delfines acoge a niños a partir de 3 años. Actividades, juegos tradicionales, camas elásticas, tirolinas, etc\r\nNatación a partir de los 4 años en piscina climatizada.\r\nPerfeccionamiento de la natación en el mar.\r\nIniciación al salvamento costero."
        ],
        "nl": [
          "De Dolphins Club verwelkomt kinderen vanaf 3 jaar. Activiteiten, traditionele spelletjes, trampolines, tokkelbanen, enz\r\nZwemmen vanaf 4 jaar in een verwarmd zwembad.\r\nPerfectioneren van zwemvaardigheden op zee.\r\nKennismaking met kustredding."
        ]
      },
